@startuml poc_architecture
title OpenSDLC PoC — 전체 아키텍처 컴포넌트 다이어그램

skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor #E8F4FD
  BorderColor #2980B9
  FontSize 11
}
skinparam package {
  BackgroundColor #FEF9E7
  BorderColor #F39C12
}
skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor #FFFDE7
  BorderColor #F9A825
}
skinparam arrow {
  Color #2C3E50
  FontSize 10
}

package "EntryPoint" {
  [run_poc.py\n(main, _save_artifacts)] as entry
}

package "Boot / Config" {
  [config.py\n─────────────\nload_dotenv()\nPROJECT_ROOT\nENGINE_DIR / CONSTITUTION_DIR\nPROMPTS_DIR / TEMPLATES_DIR\nLLM_PROVIDER / MODEL\nLLM_MAX_RETRIES\nLOG_LEVEL / LOG_LLM_IO] as config
}

package "Pipeline Engine" {
  [graph_builder.py\n─────────────\nload_pipeline_definition()\nbuild_graph_from_definition()\ncreate_pipeline()\nrun_pipeline()] as graph_builder
  [routing.py\n─────────────\nmake_validator_router()\nroute_after_validation()\n→ pass | rework | max_retries] as routing
  [state.py\n─────────────\nPipelineState (TypedDict)\nStepResult (TypedDict)\npipeline_status:\n  running | completed\n  max_retries_exceeded\n  quota_exhausted] as state
}

package "Executor" {
  [generic_agent.py\n─────────────\ncreate_agent_node() ← 팩토리\n_build_user_message()\n  ├ ReqAgent: user_story or rework\n  ├ ValidatorAgent: artifact만 전달\n  │  (context 격리 원칙)\n  ├ CodeAgent: UC+TestDesign\n  ├ TestAgent: UC or TD+Impl\n  └ CoordAgent: TestReport] as executor
}

package "Registry" {
  [agent_registry.py\n─────────────\n@lru_cache load_all_agents()\nget_agent(agent_id)] as registry
  [models.py\n─────────────\nAgentConfig\nAgentPersona\nStepDefinition\nPipelineDefinition] as models
}

package "Prompts" {
  [builder.py\n─────────────\nbuild_system_prompt()\n조립 순서 (8단계):\n1. Common Rules (AgentCommon)\n2. Agent-specific Prompt\n3. Output Templates (주출력)\n4. Validator: 5종 참조 템플릿\n   (UC/TD/Impl/TR/FB)\n5. Extra Templates (step.extra)\n6. Constitution (거버넌스)\n7. _ADVERSARIAL_MANDATE\n   (ValidatorAgent 전용)\n8. _CODE_FILE_MANDATE\n   (CodeAgent 전용)] as prompt_builder

  [loader.py\n─────────────\nload_common_prompt()\nload_agent_prompt(agent_id)\nload_template(name)\nload_constitution_excerpt()] as prompt_loader
}

package "LLM Client" {
  [llm_client.py\n─────────────\ncall_llm()\n  ├ provider routing:\n  │  _call_anthropic()\n  │  _call_google()\n  │  _call_openai()\n  ├ 내부 retry:\n  │  quality_check (min_chars)\n  │  max_retries=2 (품질 미달)\n  │  rate_limit_retries=3 (429)\n  │  _extract_retry_delay()\n  └ QuotaExhaustedError\n     (daily quota 소진)] as llm_client
}

package "Artifacts" {
  [parser.py\n─────────────\nextract_yaml_from_response()\nparse_artifact()\nget_validation_result()\nextract_artifact_id()\nextract_iteration()] as artifact_parser
  [code_extractor.py\n─────────────\nwrite_code_files()\nget_runtime_info()] as code_extractor
}

package "Config Files (Read-Only)" {
  database "pipelines/\n  poc_classic.yaml (3 steps)\n  full_spiral.yaml (9 steps)" as pipeline_yaml
  database "open-sdlc-engine/\n  agent-configs/*.config.yaml" as agent_configs
  database "open-sdlc-engine/prompts/agent/\n  AgentCommon.txt\n  ReqAgent.txt\n  ValidatorAgent.txt\n  CodeAgent.txt ..." as agent_prompts
  database "open-sdlc-engine/templates/artifacts/\n  UseCaseModelArtifact\n  ValidationReportArtifact\n  TestDesignArtifact\n  ImplementationArtifact\n  TestReportArtifact\n  FeedbackArtifact" as templates
  database "open-sdlc-constitution/\n  01-Foundation-Principles.md\n  02-Architecture-Guidelines.md ..." as constitution
}

package "LLM API (External)" {
  [Anthropic\nClaude API] as anthropic_api
  [Google\nGemini API] as google_api
  [OpenAI\nGPT API] as openai_api
}

package "Output (Runtime)" {
  database "output/iteration-N/\n  artifacts/*.yaml" as artifacts_out
  database "output/workspace/\n  (실행 가능한 코드 파일)" as workspace_out
}

' Entry connections
entry --> config : import (모듈 로드 시 자동 실행)
entry --> graph_builder : load_pipeline_definition()\nrun_pipeline()
entry --> artifact_parser : extract_artifact_id()\nextract_iteration()
entry --> code_extractor : write_code_files()
entry --> artifacts_out : YAML 파일 저장
code_extractor --> workspace_out : 코드 파일 생성

' Pipeline Engine
graph_builder --> routing : make_validator_router()
graph_builder --> executor : create_agent_node()
graph_builder --> state : PipelineState 생성
graph_builder --> models : PipelineDefinition 파싱
pipeline_yaml --> graph_builder : YAML 읽기

' Executor
executor --> registry : get_agent(agent_id)
executor --> prompt_builder : build_system_prompt()
executor --> llm_client : call_llm(system, user_msg)
executor --> artifact_parser : extract_yaml_from_response()\nget_validation_result()

' Registry
registry --> agent_configs : *.config.yaml 읽기\n(lru_cache 캐싱)
registry --> models : AgentConfig 반환

' Prompt builder
prompt_builder --> prompt_loader : 파일 로드 요청
prompt_loader --> agent_prompts : AgentCommon.txt\n각 Agent 프롬프트
prompt_loader --> templates : 아티팩트 템플릿
prompt_loader --> constitution : 거버넌스 원칙

' LLM routing
llm_client --> anthropic_api : _call_anthropic()
llm_client --> google_api : _call_google()
llm_client --> openai_api : _call_openai()

note bottom of executor
  **Context 격리 원칙**:
  ValidatorAgent에게는
  artifact YAML만 전달.
  이전 Agent의 system_prompt,
  사고 과정 미포함.
end note

note right of llm_client
  **두 가지 retry 루프**:
  1. 품질 미달 retry (max_retries=2)
     → _default_quality_check()
  2. Rate limit retry (rate_limit_retries=3)
     → 429/RESOURCE_EXHAUSTED
     → _extract_retry_delay()
  Daily quota 소진 시
  → QuotaExhaustedError 발생
  → pipeline_status="quota_exhausted"
end note

note right of prompt_builder
  **ValidatorAgent 전용 주입**:
  _ADVERSARIAL_MANDATE:
    "fail 후보 3개 먼저 열거,
     BLOCKER 없을 때만 pass"
  + 5종 참조 템플릿 (스키마 검증용)

  **CodeAgent 전용 주입**:
  _CODE_FILE_MANDATE:
    "code_files 필드 필수,
     완전한 실행 코드 포함"
end note

@enduml
